article_id:980,category_name:News,title_name:Shop Purchase Counts and Exchange Limits Refreshed!,image_path:,message:<div>We refreshed the purchase count and exchange limits for items in the shop at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1577858400"></span>!</div><div>Even if you&#39;ve already reached the purchase or exchange limit, you may now purchase or exchange for these items again.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>■Upgrade Essentials</strong></div><div>・Unbind Pack (Mana Circles)</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/cb0a7f3c1328157fd52ffb03bd389095.png"></div><div><br></div><div>・Unbind Pack (Weapons)</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/6b83fa547ae5aaf8b4be91c4c871ddfb.png"></div><div><br></div><div>・Unbind Pack (Wyrmprints)</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/d1703979bbef846beb6fd69d942f529f.png"></div><div><br></div><div>・Unbind Pack (Dragons)</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9a828ff4d0b4aeaea9ee6c5d59876569.png"></div><div><br></div><div>For information about each pack, select the shop on the Home page, then tap Upgrade Essentials &amp; Packs and select the This Month tab.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>■Treasure Trade for Astral Raids</strong></div><div>You can exchange astral shards, which can be obtained by clearing Astral Raids, for a variety of rewards.</div><div>To access the Treasure Trade for Astral Raids, select the shop on the home page, then tap Treasure Trade and check the Astral Raids section.</div><div>Note: For more information about quests where you can obtain astral shards, tap the magnifying glass icon on each Astral Raids quest, and check the Drop Rewards section that displays on the Quest Details screen.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>■Treasure Trade for Void Battles</strong></div><div>You can exchange the materials you obtain by defeating Void enemies for various rewards.</div><div>To access the Treasure Trade for Void Battles, select the shop on the home page, then tap Treasure Trade and check the Void Battles section.</div><div>Note: The exchange limits for some rewards do not reset.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1577858400,update_time1577175176